In re Resignation of Iafelice.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Iafelice (1992), 64 Ohio St.3d 1213.]

(No. 92-1363 Submitted July 29, 1992 Decided July 30, 1992.)

The resignation of Robert J. Iafelice as an attorney, Registration No. 0042441, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
